North America is anticipated for the highest revenue share during the forecast period, while the Asia Pacific region is predicted to grow at the fastest CAGR during the forecast period. BD introduced BD CellViewTM Image Technology in August 2023, which is integrated into their cell sorting devices, allowing scientists to view and categorize live cells in real time according to their visual properties.

